Preheat oven to 400 degrees F. Prepare stuffing mix as directed on package; set aside. Place chicken in 13x9-inch baking dish; cover with ham. Mix soup and mustard; spoon over chicken. Top with prepared stuffing. Bake 25 min. or until chicken is cooked through (170 degrees F). Sprinkle with cheese. Bake an additional 5 min. or until cheese is melted.